@startuml
title Feature 014 sequence - bonus wallet and transactions
actor User as "Покупатель/Партнер"
actor Finance as "Финансовый оператор"
participant Web as "React web-shell"
participant Wallet as "bonus-wallet API"
participant Order as "order module"

User -> Web: открыть /profile/transactions/:type
Web -> Wallet: GET /api/bonus-wallet/summary?type=:type
Wallet --> Web: balances, recentTransactions, applyLimit
Web -> Wallet: GET /api/bonus-wallet/transactions?filters
Wallet --> Web: transaction page
User -> Web: открыть transaction details
Web -> Wallet: GET /api/bonus-wallet/transactions/{transactionId}
Wallet --> Web: details, events, linkedResources
User -> Web: перейти к связанному заказу
Web -> Order: GET /api/order/order-history/{orderNumber}
Order --> Web: order details

Finance -> Web: создать manual adjustment
Web -> Wallet: POST /api/bonus-wallet/finance/adjustments
Wallet -> Wallet: проверить роль, reason, idempotency key
Wallet --> Web: transaction with auditRecorded=true
@enduml
